### Vegetables API (with M:N Plot Relations)

### List all vegetables
GET http://localhost:8080/vegetables
Accept: application/json

### Get vegetable by ID
GET http://localhost:8080/vegetables/1
Accept: application/json

### Create new vegetable
POST http://localhost:8080/vegetables
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Carrot",
  "nutritionalValue": 23
}

### Update vegetable
PUT http://localhost:8080/vegetables/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Carrot Deluxe",
  "nutritionalValue": 42
}

### Assign plots to vegetable (inverse M:N)
PUT http://localhost:8080/vegetables/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "plots": [
    { "id": 1 }
  ]
}

### Delete vegetable
DELETE http://localhost:8080/vegetables/1
